{"tid":2195903,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚台 高雄冰屋 伯爵茶冰","createTime":"2020-09-09T12:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T06:58:58.000Z","uid":182683,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5841fdc6b377a76c6e62eb2469ecfa11b6e9bf5e","tid":2195903,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wbUbqM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wbUbqM.jpg&h=6d9152bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6G6Quct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6G6Quct.jpg&h=d9e4d1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xcHkjc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xcHkjc.jpg&h=6b340184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩懷念緊台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以決定分享下食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIg有片～有興趣可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n名：冰屋<br />\n地址：台灣高雄市三民區綏遠一街167巷40號博愛路 原前鎮沱江街冰屋<br />\n<br />\n伯爵茶刨冰 80台幣<br />\n<br />\n先20港幣。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比屎味冰我都抵食啦。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個伯爵茶好濃，少少苦苦地唔會好甜，啲配料個芋頭正到痴曬痴，好芋。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他配料就中上水平。<br />\n<br />\n評分：10/10<br />\n溝女指數：10/10 <br />\n好多台妹打卡叫我幫佢地影相😎<br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgz2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=10849985\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgz2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=15a82026\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw</a>"},{"pid":"cda0ad2acfe4b939f03f7932645332f9470da9db","tid":2195903,"uid":200408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"好耐冇出食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIg把on9聲好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca22fa09c9d8bf6e41155c0cdbb7523b8aa79b55","tid":2195903,"uid":272819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:59:49.000Z","msg":"個冰好似影到發毛咁。。"},{"pid":"36dddc8a4134a77c3ad84d162deafad43a407ac5","tid":2195903,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cda0ad2acfe4b939f03f7932645332f9470da9db","tid":2195903,"uid":200408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"好耐冇出食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIg把on9聲好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"太耐冇去台灣 頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b417e5971bb52841e01cd87582166ce3accb8856","tid":2195903,"uid":182683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca22fa09c9d8bf6e41155c0cdbb7523b8aa79b55","tid":2195903,"uid":272819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:59:49.000Z","msg":"個冰好似影到發毛咁。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"佢真係咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一拎上黎我都嚇一嚇 問朋友係咪食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02130b80e15c190aa02cbe29e88787b1323fdb0c","tid":2195903,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"台灣師印仔幾時入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b9b130ae9342d96fed74897be1ac9a32111982","tid":2195903,